; tests/pdf-text-band.fk — LiteParse v2.1 text-extraction sibling-witness band.
;
; preludes: form-stdlib/core.fk form-stdlib/inflate.fk form-stdlib/pdf-text.fk
;
; A REAL FlateDecode PDF (produced by python zlib, structure-valid — opens in any
; viewer) carried in-recipe as bytes, so the extraction LOGIC proves four-way with
; no host I/O. pdf-text-bytes walks the stream, inflates it (the four-way inflate
; recipe), and pulls the Tj text from the `( )` operands. The file-reading lane
; (pdf-text-file / read_file_bytes) is proven three-way over .pdf-proof/*.pdf —
; host I/O is fkwu's one unsupported family, named honestly.
;
; Band verdict: 1 when the embedded PDF's text is recovered byte-for-byte.

(do
    (let pdf (list 37 80 68 70 45 49 46 52 10 49 32 48 32 111 98 106 10 60 60 32 47 84 121 112 101 32 47 67 97 116 97 108 111 103 32 47 80 97 103 101 115 32 50 32 48 32 82 32 62 62 10 101 110 100 111 98 106 10 50 32 48 32 111 98 106 10 60 60 32 47 84 121 112 101 32 47 80 97 103 101 115 32 47 75 105 100 115 32 91 51 32 48 32 82 93 32 47 67 111 117 110 116 32 49 32 62 62 10 101 110 100 111 98 106 10 51 32 48 32 111 98 106 10 60 60 32 47 84 121 112 101 32 47 80 97 103 101 32 47 80 97 114 101 110 116 32 50 32 48 32 82 32 47 77 101 100 105 97 66 111 120 32 91 48 32 48 32 54 49 50 32 55 57 50 93 32 47 67 111 110 116 101 110 116 115 32 52 32 48 32 82 32 47 82 101 115 111 117 114 99 101 115 32 60 60 32 47 70 111 110 116 32 60 60 32 47 70 49 32 53 32 48 32 82 32 62 62 32 62 62 32 62 62 10 101 110 100 111 98 106 10 52 32 48 32 111 98 106 10 60 60 32 47 76 101 110 103 116 104 32 54 52 32 47 70 105 108 116 101 114 32 47 70 108 97 116 101 68 101 99 111 100 101 32 62 62 10 115 116 114 101 97 109 10 120 218 115 10 225 210 119 51 84 48 50 81 8 73 227 50 55 82 48 55 48 80 8 73 81 208 240 72 205 201 201 215 81 112 206 207 72 45 74 205 75 78 85 240 75 45 41 207 47 202 214 211 84 8 201 226 114 13 1 0 148 56 15 159 10 101 110 100 115 116 114 101 97 109 10 101 110 100 111 98 106 10 53 32 48 32 111 98 106 10 60 60 32 47 84 121 112 101 32 47 70 111 110 116 32 47 83 117 98 116 121 112 101 32 47 84 121 112 101 49 32 47 66 97 115 101 70 111 110 116 32 47 72 101 108 118 101 116 105 99 97 32 62 62 10 101 110 100 111 98 106 10 120 114 101 102 10 48 32 54 10 48 48 48 48 48 48 48 48 48 48 32 54 53 53 51 53 32 102 32 10 48 48 48 48 48 48 48 48 48 57 32 48 48 48 48 48 32 110 32 10 48 48 48 48 48 48 48 48 53 56 32 48 48 48 48 48 32 110 32 10 48 48 48 48 48 48 48 49 49 53 32 48 48 48 48 48 32 110 32 10 48 48 48 48 48 48 48 50 52 49 32 48 48 48 48 48 32 110 32 10 48 48 48 48 48 48 48 51 55 54 32 48 48 48 48 48 32 110 32 10 116 114 97 105 108 101 114 10 60 60 32 47 83 105 122 101 32 54 32 47 82 111 111 116 32 49 32 48 32 82 32 62 62 10 115 116 97 114 116 120 114 101 102 10 52 52 54 10 37 37 69 79 70 10))
    (let expect (list 72 101 108 108 111 44 32 67 111 104 101 114 101 110 99 101 32 78 101 116 119 111 114 107 46))
    (if (list-eq (pdf-text-bytes pdf) expect) 1 0))
